1. Download Drupal from drupal.org
2. Place the files in this directory in Drupals profiles folder
3. Run the Drupal installation
4. Create a LinkedIn API KEY and enter it in the LinkedIn module configuration
5. Ask the GoXeed administrator to log in using LinkedIn from the front page
6. Go to user administration
7. Edit the user, that needs to be GoXeed administrator and check Goxeed Admin
8. Log out the Drupal Admin. It should only be use again for updates or configuration. Never for the game.
